/**
 * The Void — Dimensional Mastery System
 *
 * The skill tree formalizes the dimensional physics. No separate tree needed.
 * Each completed dimension permanently enhances the observer:
 *
 * - Better fast travel (higher β₁ = more spatial compression)
 * - Increased max HEX (health scales with β₁)
 * - Access to rarer drops (higher dimensions = better loot)
 * - Passive modifiers from dimensional understanding
 * - Faster movement through lower dimensions
 *
 * "What do you get at higher dimensionality?" — THIS.
 *
 * The skill tree is not something you choose. It's something you earn
 * by surviving dimensions. The physics rewards you naturally.
 *
 * @module @a0n/gnosis/void-dimensional-mastery
 */

